BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:E1MxgDQJPMD_a73HTUZDL
SUMMARY:Lichen Walk
DTSTAMP:20260205T082836Z
DTSTART:20260210T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Taught by Dr. Katherine Glew. Have you always wondered what lic
	hens are and why they are found on your trees\, rhododendrons and azaleas?
	 Lichens are harmless to your plants and add aesthetic value to your garde
	n. Learn about common lichens found in an urban environment and what they 
	tell us about air quality\, forest health\, geology and why they are indic
	ators of changes in the climate\, ecosystems\, and geology. You will leave
	 with a fresh understanding about lichens and a user-friendly chart that l
	ists lichens found in your neighborhood. This walk will be on trails with 
	various surfaces and may include gravel\, mulch\, or pavement. Please dres
	s for the weather and wear comfortable walking shoes. $28 BBGS members/$40
	 nonmembers.\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/lichen-walk/17923216/2026
	-02-10T00
LOCATION:Bellevue Botanical Garden\, 12001 Main St\, Bellevue\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aC01YO8baLkM4EOmr956K
SUMMARY:Global Soccer Game Webinar
DTSTAMP:20260205T082836Z
DTSTART:20260210T223000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Us for the FIFA Ready Webinar Date: February 10th\, 2:30 P
	M Location: Virtually Via Zoom Event Overview: As we gear up for the monum
	ental FIFA events\, it&'s crucial to align our regional efforts to maximiz
	e economic and infrastructural benefits. This meeting will gather key stak
	eholders from various sectors\, including our cities and business communit
	y\, to strategize and synchronize our readiness plans with an emphasis in 
	preparing our business community to ensure you are ready for this economic
	 opportunity. So do you want to learn about what resources are available t
	o you to maximize this time? Register to learn more now. These quarterly e
	vents are brought to you by the Seattle Southside Chamber of Commerce and 
	Explore Seattle Southside.  This meeting is a pivotal opportunity for stak
	eholders to collaborate and ensure our region is fully prepared to host FI
	FA events successfully. Together\, we can create a unified and effective e
	xecution plan that benefits all.\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/global-soccer-game-webina
	r/17602992/2026-02-10T00
LOCATION:Virtually via zoom\, This event will be recorded and distributed a
	fter the event to all those who register.\, Tukwila\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
